name: He(o)lliday
description:
in celebrating the new year 2022, I want to share my work entitled "He(olliday)". In this work I want to tell you about the holiday atmosphere that is like hell. Holidays that should be fun, have become scary because we are on vacation with worries about the covid 19 pandemic. What is dangerous is, instead of getting happiness, we are infected by covid.

I hope this year will be the end of "He(o)lliday"
